criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Severe and very severe COPD (postbronchodilator FEV1/FVC under 70% and FEV1 under 50%
             of the predicted value (GOLD C and D group);

          2. Inspiratory muscle weakness（Maximal Inspiratory Pressure under 60cmH2O）;

          3. Bronchial dilation test (BDT) negative

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. acute exacerbation in the previous 4 weeks;

          2. using the oral corticosteroids within 4 weeks;

          3. history of other respiratory, cardiovascular, neuromuscular, musculoskeletal diseases
             that could interfere the study.
